@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #0F172A
  LifeLineBorderColor #334155
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  ParticipantBorderColor #334155
}

title Sequence - Xem lịch chiếu

actor User as "Khách/Thành viên"
participant UI as "[[../../client/src/features/movies/pages/MovieDetailPage.tsx MovieDetailPage/SchedulePage]]"
participant Hook as "[[../../client/src/features/movies/hooks/useShowtimes.ts useShowtimes/useScheduleShowtimes]]"
participant API as "[[../../client/src/lib/api-client.ts apiClient]]"
control Ctl as "[[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/controller/showtime/ShowtimeController.java ShowtimeController]]"
participant Svc as "[[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/service/ShowtimeService.java ShowtimeService]]"
database Repo as "[[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/repo/ShowtimeRepository.java ShowtimeRepository]]"

== Xem lịch chiếu theo phim ==
User -> UI: Chọn phim cần xem lịch
UI -> Hook: [[../../client/src/features/movies/hooks/useShowtimes.ts useShowtimes({movieId})]]
Hook -> API: [[../../client/src/features/movies/hooks/useShowtimes.ts queryFn() -> apiClient.get(`/showtimes/movie/${movieId}`)]] GET /api/showtimes/movie/{movieId}
API -> Ctl: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/controller/showtime/ShowtimeController.java#L114 getShowtimesByMovie(movieId)]]
Ctl -> Svc: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/service/ShowtimeService.java getShowtimesByMovie(movieId)]]
Svc -> Repo: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/repo/ShowtimeRepository.java findByMovieId(...)]]
Repo --> Svc: List<Showtime>
Svc --> Ctl: List<ShowtimeDTO>
Ctl --> API: 200 ApiResponse<List<ShowtimeDTO>>
API --> Hook: Danh sách suất chiếu
Hook --> UI: Nhóm theo ngày và render giờ chiếu

== Xem lịch chiếu tổng quát có phân trang ==
User -> UI: Mở trang lịch chiếu tổng hợp
UI -> Hook: [[../../client/src/features/movies/hooks/useScheduleShowtimes.ts useScheduleShowtimes({page,limit,sort})]]
Hook -> API: [[../../client/src/features/movies/hooks/useScheduleShowtimes.ts getScheduleShowtimes(params)]] GET /api/showtimes?page&size&sortBy&sortDirection&fromNow=true
API -> Ctl: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/controller/showtime/ShowtimeController.java#L42 getAllShowtimes(...)]]
Ctl -> Svc: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/service/ShowtimeService.java getFutureShowtimes(pageable)]]
Svc -> Repo: [[../../src/main/java/com/mecinema/mecinema/repo/ShowtimeRepository.java findFutureShowtimes(now, pageable)]]
Repo --> Svc: Page<Showtime>
Svc --> Ctl: PaginatedResponse<ShowtimeDTO>
Ctl --> API: 200 ApiResponse<PaginatedResponse>
API --> Hook: Dữ liệu phân trang
Hook --> UI: Hiển thị lịch chiếu tương lai theo trang
@enduml
